(pRBU qoN ivikAw hoey dws vwsqy) iehI sB qoN v`fI ie`zq hY ik auh aus pRBU dw nwm dws Awpxy ihrdy ivc vsweI r`Kdw hY,
jyhVw prmwqmw sB dw ipAwrw hY qy sB dw swQI-im`qr hY ]1]
